  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "沼泽狐公司 弑君者 RMR 底座",
      "en": "Swampfox Kingslayer RMR Mount"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "SK RMR",
      "en": "SK RMR"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "沼泽狐公司的弑君者是一款经济实惠的紧凑型红点瞄准镜，以其RMR接口规格著称，非常适合直接安装在手枪滑套上。同时能安装在低矮的皮卡汀尼导轨底座令其适用于步枪和霰弹枪，故尤其受火鸡狩猎爱好者青睐。其明亮的点状或环形分划能提供快速目标捕捉能力。",
      "en": "The Swampfox Kingslayer is a budget-friendly, compact red dot sight known for its RMR footprint, making it great for direct slide mounting on pistols, while also coming with a standard low-profile Picatinny rail mount for rifles and shotguns, especially popular for turkey hunting, offering fast target acquisition with its bright dot or circle dot reticle."
    },
